---
// You vs. Them: The Tax Reality
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="section-line bg-red-500 mb-6"></div>
    <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight mb-3">
      You vs. Them: The Tax Reality
    </h2>
    <p class="font-body text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mb-10">
      Same country. Same economy. Completely different tax systems.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
      <!-- Your Side -->
      <div class="card p-6 border-t-4 border-red-500">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <span class="tag mb-3">Your Business</span>
          <div class="stat-huge text-red-600">37%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Top marginal rate for pass-through income</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Federal income tax</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-semibold">10-37%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Self-employment tax</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-semibold">15.3%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-gray-700">State income tax</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-semibold">0-13.3%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 bg-red-50 px-3 rounded-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Effective total burden</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-bold">35-45%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Their Side -->
      <div class="card p-6 border-t-4 border-blue-500">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 mb-3">Forbes 400 Billionaires</span>
          <div class="stat-huge text-blue-600">24%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Average effective rate (2018-2020)</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Capital gains preference</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-blue-600 font-semibold">20% max</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Unrealized gains</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-blue-600 font-semibold">0%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Buy-borrow-die strategy</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-blue-600 font-semibold">~0%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 bg-blue-50 px-3 rounded-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Top 25 billionaires</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-blue-600 font-bold">3.4%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Gap Visualization -->
    <div class="card p-6">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">
        On every $100,000 of income:
      </h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700">You pay</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-bold text-xl">$35,000-$45,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 40%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700">Forbes 400 average</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl">$24,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill bar-blue" style="width: 24%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700">Top 25 billionaires</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-green-600 font-bold text-xl">$3,400</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill bar-green" style="width: 3.4%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-400 mt-6 text-center">
        IRS Statistics of Income / ProPublica / Joint Committee on Taxation
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
